snippet.title: Boylei Hobby Time
snippet.description:
I’m just trying to make fun things and inspire you to be creative.

Creating an imaginary wild western world. Pioneer of the LED filament in model building.

The channel name comes from my favorite fish, Centropyge Boylei, also known as the Peppermint Angelfish. 

Boyleihobbies@gmail.com

As an Amazon Associate I earn from qualifying purchases linked in my videos.
